咪係囉"},{"pid":"57c84990daded0a28b52cc7419e511aa4abda196","tid":430703,"uid":44819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T06:04:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做會計即係要讀成世書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nNo, 我考完ACCA, HKICPA就唔讀啦....</blockquote><br />\n我唔上進都有50k，當然我係old seafood做咗十幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打條路點行 轉左幾多次工？或者做邊個area嘅acct？"},{"pid":"6b3738224256a06df18e202272634107c5d83e09","tid":430703,"uid":119959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T06:20:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做會計即係要讀成世書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nNo, 我考完ACCA, HKICPA就唔讀啦....</blockquote><br />\n我唔上進都有50k，當然我係old seafood做咗十幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打條路點行 轉左幾多次工？或者做邊個area嘅acct？</blockquote><br />\n我係唔進取型, 有50k已好滿足😊,<br />\n有進取D嘅都有6-70k....<br />\nibank local finance 轉 regional finance, 轉捩點就係考左個牌, regional team就搵咗入去啦"},{"pid":"2fb835197dbaf3616f0ff6bd1cf480daa463e662","tid":430703,"uid":110758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T06:24:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>每間公司都需要會計</blockquote><br />\n無牌既話成世人都係係萬鬆啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實都係睇你際遇<br />\n以前做sme audit都成日見到D客個會計<br />\n冇牌 冇big4經驗 盤數入到亂一亂既<br />\n依然逗緊兩萬幾三萬人工<br />\n唔知點解會有D老細比個會計食返住 唔敢炒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8054d52472d02463059dbd31454da6fc34c91847","tid":430703,"uid":126566,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T06:27:12.000Z","msg":"big4咪人係入面人人想出去 出面既人想入去<br />\n起碼我覺得暫時audit方面未咁快有AI取代 同埋都未算夕陽 起碼有rule/IRD監管住一年至少做1次audit<br />\n同埋好多延伸會比傳統audit/acc好搵, 特別做assets management / related to financial的公司 或者稅務方面"},{"pid":"6d8d134ad8300530118bf06eb8d09cb3cbc32a21","tid":430703,"uid":119959,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T07:01:40.000Z","msg":"老生常談, 公作態度, 攪好關係...<br />\n兩三次轉team都係D team head 問我有無興趣轉 （finance入面好L多team做唔同野)<br />\n有個同期嘅而家仲做緊local finance, 做野怕蝕底, 又考唔到牌, 都唔知有無25k"},{"pid":"8d16b21d0b31500c724f39a641265b9da64d82e4","tid":430703,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T07:12:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d72cfbd74b3b3869ecc637187729712c3a80e885","tid":430703,"uid":48521,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T09:33:38.000Z","msg":"做佐一年 無牌<br />\n廿k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e0107015b456e55f0b41de878a323a76749802","tid":430703,"uid":119959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T09:40:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做佐一年 無牌<br />\n廿k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGood start👍"},{"pid":"2083afd7deab1c176b5c681bac7cd6e5228ed2a5","tid":430703,"uid":40695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T09:40:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老生常談, 公作態度, 攪好關係...<br />\n兩三次轉team都係D team head 問我有無興趣轉 （finance入面好L多team做唔同野)<br />\n有個同期嘅而家仲做緊local finance, 做野怕蝕底, 又考唔到牌, 都唔知有無25k</blockquote><br />\n想問搞好關係即係點？"},{"pid":"bc5849bbe27ac38e372412ca6a2712a403b5e409","tid":430703,"uid":107350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T09:52:10.000Z","msg":"你係有料既話做咩都有前途架啦"}]}